DescDetail: << 
Library to add a query engine to C applications.
A SQL database is not needed; any collection of C/C++ objects can
act as tables. QOF is the gnucash engine with all the financial
objects removed. Used by GnuCash, pilot-qof and GnoTime.
Supports SQL-type queries and includes a generic XML backend.
<<
DescPackaging: <<
Use pkg-config (name: qof-1 ) to obtain the libdir and xmldir variables
--variable=libdir --variable=xmldir to load the backend and validate XML.
For more information, see http://qof.sourceforge.net/hacking.html
<<
